VANGERS: One for the Road
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

1. Required libraries:

   - SDL
   - SDL_net
   - libvorbis
   - clunk (http://media.netive.ru/clunk/)
   - ffmpeg
   - zlib

2. Required tools:

   - cmake
   - make

3. Building:

   $ mkdir build
   $ cd build
   $ cmake ..
   $ make

4. Running:

   $ cd data
   $ ../build/src/vangers
